<link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/home.css" />
<div class="index-container">
  <div class="inner-container">
    <div>
      <div class="index-header">NurdCollab</div>
      <div class="index-intro">
        Nurd let nerds create cloud room where they can can collaborate with
        other nerds and work on any project with real time editor and real time
        communication. Just a step to ease the lives of nerd community...
      </div>
      <div class="index-animation">
        <div class="join-container">
          <input
            id="myInput"
            type="text"
            placeholder="Room ID: xxxx-xxxx-xxxx-xxxx"
          />
        </div>
        <div class="cnct">
          <a
            id="join"
            class="connect sign-up"
            onclick="myFunction()"
            href="/users/"
            >Join</a
          >
          <p style="font-size: 1.5rem">--or--</p>
          <a class="connect sign-in" href="/users/">Create</a>
          <!-- <a class = "connect" href="/users/"><div class="sign-in">Create</div></a>-->
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="index-animation">
      <div class="image">
        <img class="image" src="/images/coding.png" alt="a" />
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="feature-container">
    <h1>What NurdCollab offers you?</h1>

    <div class="feature-items">
      <div class="theme">
        <h3>Choose what suits your eyes<br /></h3>
        <img src="/images/OIP.jfif" alt="theme-img" />
        <p>
          <br />Whether you are a dark theme lover or light theme lover, we have
          got you. Choose from a variety of editor theme"
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="lang">
        <h3>Language syntax support<br /></h3>
        <img src="/images/langimg.jpg" alt="laguage-img" />
        <p>
          <br />NurdCollab supports many programming languages syntax with many
          intellisence features for almost every language to help you
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="communication">
        <h3>Realtime communication<br /></h3>
        <img src="/images/Remote working.png" alt="communication-img" />
        <p>
          <br />Nurdcollab is not just a code editor! Here you can communicate
          with your fellow coder via video-conferencing for better productivity
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="offer">
      <div class="left-side">
        <img src="/images/collab1.png" alt="collab-img" />
      </div>
      <div class="right-side">
        <!--h2>What it offers</h2-->
        <h1>Collaborate with your mates</h1>
        <br />
        <p>
          "No matter how far you are from your mates now you can collaborate and
          work with your mates at same place using NurdCollab"
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

 

    
  </div>
  <script>
    function myFunction() {
      var inputVal = document.getElementById("myInput").value;
      var anchor = document.getElementById("join");
      anchor.href = anchor.href + inputVal;
    }
